title: What Does Your Inner Voice *Really* Sound Like?
description:
If you haven't heard, Moe has a podcast – “In The Moement” - and every week he covers a variety of topics.
In his latest episode, Moe asked Romeo and Keity about their internal monologue. He always thought that everyone's inner voice sounded like their normal voice, but that's not the case.
What does your inner voice sound like?
